其.definition: his; her; its; their; that; such; it (refers to sth preceding it)

其一.definition: one of the given (options etc); the first; firstly

其二.definition: secondly; the other (usu. of two); the second

其他.definition: other; (sth or sb) else; the rest

其來有自.definition: there is a reason for it; (of sth) not incidental

其先.definition: previously; before that; up to then

其外.definition: besides; in addition; apart from that

其所.definition: its place; one's appointed place; the place for that

其貌不揚.definition: (idiom) nothing special to look at; unprepossessing

其間.definition: in between; within that interval; in the meantime

其餘.definition: the rest; the others; remaining; remainder; apart from them
